    "description": "特工，紧急情况。<br>敌人已经启动了大规模的电磁脉冲武器的发射器。接下来你需要回收散落在敌人各个基地的电磁脉冲武器的中止代码。<br>这将是一次单独的潜入任务，祝你好运。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2298210/extras/28e77b33f84e9342af89c1f0f238b693.poster.avif?t=1678946115\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2298210/extras/28e77b33f84e9342af89c1f0f238b693.webm?t=1678946115\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2298210/extras/28e77b33f84e9342af89c1f0f238b693.mp4?t=1678946115\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>本作是一款俯视视角的射击动作游戏，玩家需要扮演一位女高中生模样的特工潜入基地进行战斗。<br>每个关卡（“层级”）都有各种各样的地形和敌人在等着你。<br>玩家需要即时做出决定，但务必找到其中的最优解。<br><br>届时会为你提供一些装备，以协助潜入。<br>是生是死，取决于你。<br><br><u>- 反转能力 -</u><br>使用这个能力可以反转自己和敌人的子弹判定，同时反弹附近的子弹。<br>这是一个摆脱窘境的关键能力，一定要谨慎使用。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2298210/extras/d528a0c16c59bc1a5fdf65df12aa9b21.poster.avif?t=1678946115\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2298210/extras/d528a0c16c59bc1a5fdf65df12aa9b21.webm?t=1678946115\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2298210/extras/d528a0c16c59bc1a5fdf65df12aa9b21.mp4?t=1678946115\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><u>- 投掷物品 -</u><br>这个能力可以投掷障碍物，即一种如同念力的招式。<br>可以随意将其用作掩护或者武器。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2298210/extras/32a4d82f5c37ef80dc2391fac0209793.poster.avif?t=1678946115\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2298210/extras/32a4d82f5c37ef80dc2391fac0209793.webm?t=1678946115\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2298210/extras/32a4d82f5c37ef80dc2391fac0209793.mp4?t=1678946115\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><u>- 冲刺滑行 -</u><br>这个能力可以穿过对手的子弹，同时进行高速移动。<br>这是一个攻守兼具的能力，看准时机出招吧。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2298210/extras/6f3e9b9ffa21f4b4c5b1c9269216f3ca.poster.avif?t=1678946115\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2298210/extras/6f3e9b9ffa21f4b4c5b1c9269216f3ca.webm?t=1678946115\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2298210/extras/6f3e9b9ffa21f4b4c5b1c9269216f3ca.mp4?t=1678946115\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>——————各种极致玩法——————</strong><br><u>“换装”</u><br>在执行任务期间居然还在意自己的打扮，真是不成熟呢。<br>好吧，如果你能证明自己有相当的能力，我就考虑一下吧。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2298210/extras/27a3a04280cce88c7888d8080545dca0.poster.avif?t=1678946115\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2298210/extras/27a3a04280cce88c7888d8080545dca0.webm?t=1678946115\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2298210/extras/27a3a04280cce88c7888d8080545dca0.mp4?t=1678946115\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><u>“新武器”</u><br>开展行动显然需要武器。<br>那就在挑战新的关卡层级的时候，试试看提供的武器吧。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2298210/extras/7a4a53b4ae0f00c9769395657072ea0d.poster.avif?t=1678946115\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2298210/extras/7a4a53b4ae0f00c9769395657072ea0d.webm?t=1678946115\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2298210/extras/7a4a53b4ae0f00c9769395657072ea0d.mp4?t=1678946115\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><u>“进阶挑战”</u><br>在“双击毙命”以及“单击毙命”模式下，一个过失足以致命。<br>可是，如果攻克成功，也就证明你的实力强大，我期待你的表现喔。",
